imes New Roman'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\";font-family:'微软雅黑',sans-serif\">周燕珉<span>, </span><strong>秦岭</strong><span>. </span>老龄化背景下城市新旧住宅的适老化转型<span>[J]. </span>时代建筑<span>, 2016, 06: 22-28.</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:3px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:56px;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left\"><span><span style=\";font-family:'微软雅黑',sans-serif\"><span>[15] <span style=\"font:9px 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><strong><span style=\";font-family:'微软雅黑',sans-serif\">秦岭</span></strong></span><span><span style=\";font-family:'微软雅黑',sans-serif\">. </span></span><span><span style=\";font-family:'微软雅黑',sans-serif\">学术研究探讨<span>——</span>养老设施居室设计的常见误区与建议<span>[J]. </span>建筑知识<span>·</span>医养环境设计<span>, 2016, 07: 27-29.</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:3px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:56px;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left\"><span><span style=\";font-family:'微软雅黑',sans-serif\"><span>[16] <span style=\"font:9px 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><strong><span style=\";font-family:'微软雅黑',sans-serif\">秦岭</span></strong></span><span><span style=\";font-family:'微软雅黑',sans-serif\">. </span></span><span><span style=\";font-family:'微软雅黑',sans-serif\">设计优化点评<span>——</span>养老设施辅助服务空间设计优化案例<span>[J]. </span>建筑知识<span>·</span>医养环境设计<span>, 2016, 05: 98-99.</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:3px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:56px;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left\"><span><span style=\";font-family:'微软雅黑',sans-serif\"><span>[17] <span style=\"font:9px 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\";font-family:'微软雅黑',sans-serif\">周燕珉<span>, </span><strong>秦岭</strong><span>. </span>日本养老设施的设计经验总结<span>[J].</span>世界建筑导报<span>, 2015, 30(03): 30-33.</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:3px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:56px;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left\"><span style=\";font-family:'微软雅黑',sans-serif\"><span>[18] <span style=\"font:9px 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><strong><span style=\";font-family:'微软雅黑',sans-serif\">Qin Ling</span></strong><span style=\";font-family:'微软雅黑',sans-serif\">. Research Framework, Questions and Methods of Home Modification for the Elderly Based on Environment-behavior Theory[C]// the 15th International Conference on Environment-Behavior Studies, 2022-11-18~20, Beijing Jiaotong University, Beijing.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:3px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:56px;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left\"><span style=\";font-family:'微软雅黑',sans-serif\"><span>[19] <span style=\"font:9px 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><strong><span style=\";font-family:'微软雅黑',sans-serif\">Qin Ling</span></strong><span style=\";font-family:'微软雅黑',sans-serif\">. A Study on the Influence of Home Modification on the Behaviors of Elderly People: Take the Bathroom as an Example[C]//Zou Guangtian, Wang Yan. A New Idea for Starting Point of the Silk Road: Urban and Rural Design for Human: Proceedings of the 14th International Conference on Environment-Behavior Studies. Wuhan: Huazhong University of Science &amp; Technology Press, 2020: 1530-1536.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top:3px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:56px;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left\"><span style=\";font-family:'微软雅黑',sans-serif\"><span>[20] <span style=\"font:9px 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><strong><span style=\";font-family:'微软雅黑',sans-serif\">秦岭</span></strong><span style=\";font-family:'微软雅黑',sans-serif\">. “</span><span style=\";font-family:'微软雅黑',sans-serif\">医养结合<span>”</span>背景下养老机构医疗服务资源的配置使用状况与现存问题分析<span>——</span>以北京市为例<span>[C]//</span>中国老年学和老年医学学会<span>2020</span>年学术大会，<span>2020-11-07~08</span>，中国老年学和老年医学学会，广西南宁<span>.</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:3px;text-align:left\"><span style=\";font-family:'微软雅黑',sans-s